{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have enough context to make the extension concrete. Plan: 1. Extend the durable outline model and save path so outline revisions can classify edit impact, preserve per-card purpose/order metadata, and support single-card regeneration w...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_57", "text": "I have enough context to make the extension concrete. Plan:\n1. Extend the durable outline model and save path so outline revisions can classify edit impact, preserve per-card purpose/order metadata, and support single-card regeneration without touching the whole beat sheet.\n2. Rework the `StorySetupStage` outline area into a real card editor: visible cards with reorder controls, editable structured fields, per-card regenerate, and explicit downstream impact messaging.\n3. Expand backend and frontend tests around outline saves, impact classification, and editor interactions, then run the targeted suites plus broader build/lint checks.\n4. Run browser-based visual QA against the Docker Compose app, capture screenshots, and only then write the required reviewer summary file as the final filesystem change.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 114, "prompt_index": 55, "prompt_name": "54 \u2014 Chapter and Scene Card Editor", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T03:14:35-07:00"}
