p the planner balance pacing, chapter shape, and read-aloud feel. They are honest suggestions, not hard guarantees.\"\n          label=\"Expectation setting\"\n          title=\"Guides, not guarantees\"\n        >\n          <div className=\"workspace-stage-detail__badges\">\n            <Badge tone=\"brand\">Soft targets</Badge>\n            <Badge tone=\"neutral\">Bedtime-first</Badge>\n          </div>\n        </SummaryPanel>\n\n        <SummaryPanel\n          description={\n            downstreamLabels.length > 0\n              ? `${downstreamLabels.join(', ')} may need another pass after these targets change.`\n              : 'No later stages depend on this step.'\n          }\n          label=\"Next step\"\n          title={\n            hasSavedOutline\n              ? 'Composition can use this outline'\n              : snapshot.selected_story_setup != null\n                ? 'Save targets to rebuild the outline'\n                : 'Save to unlock composition planning'\n          }\n        >\n          <div className=\"cta-row\">\n            <Button\n              disabled={!hasSavedOutline}\n              onClick={() => {\n                onPreviewStage('composition')\n              }}\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '760,840p' frontend/src/features/session/StorySetupStage.tsx\"", "exit_code": 0, "id": "item_111", "status": "completed", "type": "command_execution"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 224, "prompt_index": 55, "prompt_name": "54 \u2014 Chapter and Scene Card Editor", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T03:25:05-07:00"}
