{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Finished", "message": "completed, exit 0: /bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '2230,2305p' frontend/src/styles/index.css\"", "raw_event": {"item": {"aggregated_output": "  gap: var(--space-4);\n}\n\n.story-setup-stage__heuristic,\n.story-setup-stage__suggestion {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n}\n\n.story-setup-stage__heuristic p,\n.story-setup-stage__suggestion p {\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.story-setup-stage__suggestion {\n  padding: 0.85rem 0.95rem;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);\n  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(39, 69, 99, 0.08);\n}\n\n.story-outline-stage__cards {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  list-style: none;\n}\n\n.story-outline-stage__card {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n  padding: 1rem 1.05rem;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  background:\n    linear-gradient(\n      180deg,\n      rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.96),\n      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82)\n    ),\n    var(--color-surface-strong);\n  box-shadow:\n    inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(169, 116, 60, 0.12),\n    0 14px 32px rgba(39, 69, 99, 0.08);\n}\n\n.story-outline-stage__card-header {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n}\n\n.story-outline-stage__card-header h4,\n.story-outline-stage__card p {\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n.story-brief-stage__preview {\n  display: grid;\n  gap: var(--space-3);\n  padding: var(--space-3);\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  background:\n    linear-gradient(\n      180deg,\n      rgba(255, 250, 242, 0.96),\n      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82)\n    ),\n    var(--color-surface-strong);\n  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(169, 116, 60, 0.12);\n}\n\n.story-brief-stage__preview-section {\n  padding: 0.9rem 1rem;\n  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);\n", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '2230,2305p' frontend/src/styles/index.css\"", "exit_code": 0, "id"