evin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-22-workspace-desktop.png) and [prompt-22-workspace-mobile.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-22-workspace-mobile.png); the desktop chat pane measured `0.328` of the shell width, and mobile stacked cleanly. The only verification limit was a pre-existing compose backend blocker from the local `secrets.yaml` schema, so the browser run used intercepted API responses against the live Vite app instead of a fully live backend container.\"}}\n./prompts/28-error-loading-and-feedback-states.codex.jsonlines:5:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_1\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -lc \\\"pwd && rg --files . | sed 's#\\\"'^./##'\\\"' | rg '(\\\"'^frontend/|''^webui/|package.json$|docker-compose|compose|AGENTS'\\\"\\\\\\\\.md\\\"'$|README|prompts/28-error-loading-and-feedback-states'\\\"\\\\\\\\.md\\\"'$)'\\\"'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"/Users/kevin/code/storyteller\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.codex.jsonlines\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.yolopilot.jsonlines\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.yolopilot.md\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.md\\nprompts/96-compose-dev-and-prod-shapes.md\\nprompts/04-docker-compose-foundation.summary.md\\nprompts/28-error-loading-and-feedback-states.md\\nscripts/dev-compose.sh\\nscripts/README.md\\nREADME.md\\ndocs/README.md\\ndocs/adr/README.md\\nbackend/README.md\\nbackend/app/worker/README.md\\ntools/README.md\\ntest-assets/README.md\\ntools/webapp-qa/package.json\\nbackend/migrations/README.md\\nfrontend/tsconfig.app.json\\nfrontend/index.html\\nfrontend/tsconfig.node.json\\nfrontend/Dockerfile\\nfrontend/README.md\\nfrontend/tsconfig.json\\nfrontend/package.json\\nfrontend/package-lock.json\\nfrontend/vite.config.ts\\nfrontend/eslint.config.js\\nfrontend/vitest.config.ts\\nfrontend/public/favicon.svg\\ninfra/persistence/README.md\\ninfra/README.md\\nfrontend/src/state/appShellStore.ts\\ninfra/com