{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the chapter/scene card editor end to end. The backend now classifies outline revisions, supports selective card regeneration, persists outline edit history/impact metadata, and hydrates that back to the UI; the frontend now s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_201", "text": "Implemented the chapter/scene card editor end to end. The backend now classifies outline revisions, supports selective card regeneration, persists outline edit history/impact metadata, and hydrates that back to the UI; the frontend now shows a real card rail with purpose, linked beats, target lengths, reorder controls, an editor panel, and explicit minor vs structural invalidation messaging. The main code landed in commit `6507cc3`, and the required reviewer summary is written at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/54_chapter_and_scene_card_editor/summary.md).\n\nVerification completed with `ruff check`, `python -m compileall backend/app`, `pytest backend/tests/test_outline_generation_service.py backend/tests/test_story_tools.py -q`, `pytest backend/tests/test_session_api.py -q`, `npm --prefix frontend run lint`, `npm --prefix frontend run build`, and targeted Vitest runs for `StorySetupStage` and `SessionWorkspacePage`. Browser QA ran against the compose stack at `infra/compose/docker-compose.yml`, including a live story-setup session at desktop and mobile sizes plus a reorder interaction that surfaced the structural-change warning; screenshots are at `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-54-outline-editor-desktop.png`, `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-54-outline-editor-reordered.png`, and `/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-54-outline-editor-mobile.png`.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 425, "prompt_index": 55, "prompt_name": "54 \u2014 Chapter and Scene Card Editor", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T03:38:51-07:00"}
